          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="use-case-card">
          <div class="use-case-icon">
            <svg width="32" height="32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path d="M19 21V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v16m14 0h2m-2 0h-5m-9 0H3m2 0h5M9 7h1m-1 4h1m4-4h1m-1 4h1m-5 10v-5a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v5m-4 0h4"/>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="use-case-title">合规要求高</h3>
          <p class="use-case-description">
            需要满足严格数据合规要求，数据不能流出服务器
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Pricing Section -->
  <section class="pricing section-lg" id="pricing">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-header">
        <h2 class="section-title">方案与定价</h2>
        <p class="section-description">一次性投入，永久使用。告别按量付费，长期节约成本 80%+</p>
      </div>
      <div class="pricing-grid">
        <!-- Software License -->
        <div class="pricing-card featured">
          <div class="pricing-badge-featured">核心产品</div>
          <div class="pricing-header">
            <h3 class="pricing-title">软件授权</h3>
            <div class="pricing-badge">一次性买断</div>
          </div>
          <div class="pricing-price">
            <span class="price-currency">¥</span>
            <span class="price-value">128,000</span>
          </div>
          <ul class="pricing-features">
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
              所有功能无限制使用
            </li>
            <li>
              <svg width="20" height="20" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10 18a8 8 0 100-16 8 8 0 000 16zm3.707-9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414-1.414L9 10.586 7.707 9.293a1 1 0 00-1.414 1.414l2 2a1 1 0 001.414 0l4-4z" clip-rule="evenodd"/>
              </svg>
